Halloween party today.

40:56.541 --> 40:59.021
She insisted on going
dressed as Judge Lola.

40:59.065 --> 41:01.284
Your friend lets
his third grader

41:01.328 --> 41:03.112
watch coverage
of a murder trial?

41:03.156 --> 41:04.374
Calm down. She probably
thought you were someone

41:04.418 --> 41:06.638
from "Harry Potter."
- [ snickers ]

41:06.681 --> 41:07.900
Seriously, though,

41:07.943 --> 41:10.424
you just became
that little girl's Uhura.

41:10.468 --> 41:13.819
[ Meghan Linsey's "Lover"
playing ]

41:13.862 --> 41:16.386
♪♪♪

41:16.430 --> 41:18.737
I got your message.
What's up?

41:18.780 --> 41:20.521
In here.

41:20.565 --> 41:22.697
♪♪♪

41:22.741 --> 41:24.830
My own personal
study room?

41:24.873 --> 41:28.790
It's quiet. No one
will know you're here.

41:28.834 --> 41:30.662
[ chuckles ]

41:30.705 --> 41:32.794
You put all this
together for me?

41:32.838 --> 41:34.143
You gave up your study time

41:34.187 --> 41:35.754
so that couple could have
their special night.

41:35.797 --> 41:39.235
You are a good man,
Luke Watkins.

41:39.279 --> 41:42.412
It's about time someone did
something nice for you, so...

41:42.456 --> 41:46.373
Time to hit the books,
I guess.

41:46.416 --> 41:48.506
Good luck.

41:48.549 --> 41:51.509
♪ ...by flying through
my pain♪

41:51.552 --> 41:53.293
Thank you.

