♪ L-o, l-o, l-o-v-e-r♪

41:59.691 --> 42:02.650
♪ L-o, l-o, l-o-v-e-r♪

42:02.694 --> 42:05.653
♪♪♪

42:05.697 --> 42:09.178
- Well, I'll let you get to it.
- No. Studying can wait.

42:09.222 --> 42:10.658
What? I'm not gonna be
the reason

42:10.702 --> 42:13.269
you fail your exams.

42:13.313 --> 42:15.315
[ inhales deeply ]
Thank you, though.

42:15.358 --> 42:16.490
That was...

42:16.534 --> 42:17.970
♪♪♪

42:18.013 --> 42:20.407
That was really nice.

